== 评价与影响 ==
{{expand section|time=2018-01-28}}

本剧于2005年8月29日首播时曾达到约10.5百万人次的收视。Fox台自从数年前的《{{link-en|飞越情海|Melrose Place}}》和《[[艾莉的異想世界|艾莉的異想世界]]》以来未曾有过如此佳绩。该剧在18-49岁与18-34岁的年龄段收视[[社会统计调查|调查]]中均位居排行首位<ref name="Variety-2005sep07">{{cite news|first=Rick |last=Kissell |title=Everyone's watching Post-Katrina coverage |url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117928712 |work=''[[综艺_(杂志)|Variety]]'' |language=en |date=2005-09-07 |accessdate=2009-01-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629172453/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117928712 |archivedate=2011-06-29 }}</ref>。伴随着首播的高收视率而来的，还有众多的好评。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》评论《越狱》是“比绝大多数新剧集更加吸引人，并且也是最具原创性的作品之一”，赞其创造了一种“悬疑惊悚剧”，并且欣赏它“写实化的观感”（"authentic look"）<ref name="TNYT-2005aug29">{{cite news|first=Alessandra |last=Stanley |title=Jailhouse Heroes Are Hard to Find |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2005/08/29/arts/television/29stan.html |work=''[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]'' |language=en |date=2005-08-29 |accessdate=2009-01-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130223004409/http://www.nytimes.com/2005/08/29/arts/television/29stan.html |archivedate=2013-02-23 }}</ref>。《[[Entertainment_Weekly|娱乐周刊]]》的吉联·福莱恩（Gillian Flynn）赞它为2005年度最佳新剧之一<ref name="EW-2006apr21">{{cite news|first=Gillian |last=Flynn |title=TV Review: Prison Break (2005) |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,1186037,00.html |work=''[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]'' |language=en |date=2006-04-21 |accessdate=2009-01-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090119055611/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C1186037%2C00.html |archivedate=2009-01-19 }}</ref>。另一方面，《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》批评该剧具有“阴郁压抑的狂妄主义”（"somber pretentiousness"）和“不一致地过誉”（"uniformly overwrought"）表现<ref name="TWP-2005aug29">{{cite news|first=Tom |last=Shales |title='Prison Break': Sharpen Up Those Spoons |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/08/28/AR2005082801134.html |work=''[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]]'' |language=en |date=2005-08-29 |accessdate=2009-01-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20051026084135/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/08/28/AR2005082801134.html |archivedate=2005-10-26}}</ref>。因大获好评，Fox决定将《越狱》第1季延长9集，使其成为2005-2006年度首部达到22集长度的剧集<ref name="Variety-2005sep28">{{cite news|first=Josef |last=Adalian |title=Fox fine with more jail time |url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117929907?refCatId=1417 |work=''Variety'' |language=en |date=2005-09-28 |accessdate=2009-01-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629172522/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117929907?refCatId=1417 |archivedate=2011-06-29}}</ref>。本剧第1季获得约9.2百万人次的周平均收视率<ref name="THR-2006may26"/>。

《越狱》第一季在中国大陆获得了观看热潮<ref name="华媒网1"/><ref name="第二季暂停"/>，而且产生了在中国比在美国更受欢迎的现象<ref name="在中国更受欢迎"/>。截止2017年初，由[[搜狐|搜狐]]购买的前4季正版视频的在线观看次数也超过9亿次<ref name="在中国更受欢迎"/>。

